                   input/output pairs with     or rule that affects the
                   complete member data and    fixture's expected outputs.
                   all expected outputs.       

  **Statutory      Early retirement reduction  Legislative change to the
  Tables**         lookup tables (RMC          Revised Municipal Code.
                   §18-409(b)). Implemented as These change very
                   lookup, not formula, per    infrequently.
