  ------------------ -------------------------- --------------------------

> *The diagnosis "code is correct, test is wrong" requires extra
> scrutiny. It is the most common rationalization for suppressing
> legitimate defects. Require statutory citation proving the code's
> output is correct before modifying any oracle.*

