9\. Framework Governance

9.1 Relationship to Other Layers

  ------------------------ ----------------------------------------------
  **Layer**                **Interface with This Framework**

  **Layer 1: Prevention**  Feeds test case requirements via the Rule
                           Change SDLC. Design review checklists require
                           test plan before implementation begins. CIA
                           identifies regression scope.

  **Layer 3: Dashboard**   Consumes test execution results, coverage
                           metrics, and failure reports. Displays
                           real-time build status and trend analysis.

  **Layer 4: Resolution**  Receives classified defects from failure
                           handling. Provides resolution status back to
                           re-run verification.

  **Layer 5: Taxonomy**    Supplies the classification vocabulary used in
                           failure reports. Receives new defect category
                           proposals when failures don't fit existing
                           categories.
  ------------------------ ----------------------------------------------

